<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I loved the part where Thalia and Markos become friends when Thalia shows him how to make a camera. The countdown while the picture is being taken, in<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I loved the part where Thalia and Markos become friends when Thalia shows him how to make a camera. The countdown while the picture is being taken, interspersed with future events is so beautiful. I also loved Marko's mother's attitude and action regarding Thalia. Marko's mother taught Thalia and Markos so much about how to face life.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
